    { question: "What exactly is AI SMS messaging for tradesmen?", answer: "AI SMS messaging for tradesmen gives every skilled trade business � whatever your speciality � an intelligent text response system that works 24/7 while you work on-site. Customers increasingly text tradesmen because it\'s quicker than calling, allows photo sharing, and creates a written record they can reference. The AI handles every incoming text with a personalised response that references the specific job described. When someone texts \'garden fence blown down in the wind, can you replace it?\' with photos of the damage, the AI acknowledges the specific problem, references the images, and confirms you\'ll be in touch with a quote. For tradesmen who receive 5-15 text enquiries per week but can\'t respond while operating power tools, carrying materials, or working at height, the AI ensures every single message gets a professional, immediate response that stops the customer from texting your competitors." },
