 a fitter, an installer, a repairer, a maintenance professional, a handyman, a multi-trade operative, or a self-employed sole trader � the AI handles every text message your business receives. It covers every type of trade enquiry: emergency callouts, repair requests, installation quotations, maintenance contracts, property surveys, fault reports, upgrade consultations, insurance work, commercial contracts, landlord portfolios, new build specifications, and planned project work. The AI responds to every text � from a quick 'are you available Saturday?' to a detailed project brief with photos � and delivers the complete lead to your phone, ready for your expert follow-up." },
    { question: "Can your AI receptionist handle photo messages?", answer: "Yes. If a customer sends a photo of a leak, a broken lock, or damage to their property, your AI receptionist acknowledges the image and continues qualifying the lead. The photo is included in the lead summary sent to you." },
    { question: "Does the customer know they're texting an AI?", answer: "Your AI receptionist responds naturally and professionally. Most customers assume they're texting a receptionist or office manager. The experience feels completely human." },
